		(company "Private / Custom Drone Hardware")
		(comment 1 "Top-Level Hierarchical Sheet - Baseband/Frontend Architecture")
		(comment 2 "GPS L1 (1.575 GHz) + Wi-Fi/ISM (2.4 GHz)")
		(comment 3 "14.8V 4S LiPo Power Source")
		(comment 4 "Thermal Failsafe + GaN Bias Sequencing")
	)
	(lib_symbols)
	(text "jamRF-v2: High-Power Chaos-Modulated Jammer\nBaseband / Frontend Architecture (HackRF One style)\n\nGPS L1 (1.575 GHz) + Wi-Fi/ISM (2.4 GHz)\n\nSystem Architecture:\n- Baseband: ESP32 controller, chaos modulation DAC outputs\n- Frontend GPS: VCO -> Atten -> BPF -> GaN PA -> Isolator -> SMA\n- Frontend WiFi: VCO -> Atten -> BPF -> WiFi PA -> Isolator -> SMA\n- Power: Battery, buck, LDO, charge pump, MOSFET switches\n- Control: Thermal failsafe, bias sequencing, RF shielding\n\n4-Layer FR4, 0.062\", 1oz Cu, 50-ohm controlled impedance"
